  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bright white light, the hero wakes up and sees a crystal in front of him, he realises he must find the others, and restore the greatness of his settlement! Where are all the people? He takes a simple sword and goes to the nearest island in search of the people...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FROM NOTHING TO SOMETHING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From one almost forgotten to a thriving kingdom, build greatness with your allies. Use building tools to create the perfect stronghold. Construct, furnish and decorate your new home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.mp4?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CREATE YOUR DESTINY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your randomly-generated islands. Find treasures, equipment, survivors. Fight with evil and create a better future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.mp4?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE RAIDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build unbreakable defenses and set traps against unrelenting waves of enemies. Arm your settlers and command them in battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/7ac7d481b78da5c31a26ebcae6bcaaa5.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=609 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/7ac7d481b78da5c31a26ebcae6bcaaa5.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bright white light, the hero wakes up and sees a crystal in front of him, he realises he must find the others, and restore the greatness of his settlement! Where are all the people? He takes a simple sword and goes to the nearest island in search of the people...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FROM NOTHING TO SOMETHING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From one almost forgotten to a thriving kingdom, build greatness with your allies. Use building tools to create the perfect stronghold. Construct, furnish and decorate your new home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.mp4?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CREATE YOUR DESTINY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your randomly-generated islands. Find treasures, equipment, survivors. Fight with evil and create a better future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.mp4?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE RAIDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build unbreakable defenses and set traps against unrelenting waves of enemies. Arm your settlers and command them in battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/7ac7d481b78da5c31a26ebcae6bcaaa5.poster.avif?t=1772677838\" width=609 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/7ac7d481b78da5c31a26ebcae6bcaaa5.webm?t=1772677838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
